snippet.title: Retro Sonic - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Retro Sonic is a Sonic the Hedgehog fangame by Christian Whitehead, who is behind the Android ports of Sonic the Hedgehog, Sonic the Hedgehog 2 and Sonic the Hedgehog CD.

Download: http://www.mediafire.com/download/5qwiwc7d49w3vu9
